TopicTitle: Losing my mind, what Mod causes the "Error" "Engine disabled: Catastrophic overheating imminent!"

Articles.Content:
Title. Had to reset my PC, luckily I had a mod list. After installing all my mods again, I noticed most engines shut down because of the error above. I have no Idea what mod is causing this. Even with Cheats. Maybe CKAN installed some dependency that wasn't present before. Could someone tell me what mod is causing this issue?

 

Thanks.
